Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Sebaste Central School in the Municipality of Sebaste, Province of Antique, to Juan O. Dela Cruz Memorial School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 739
An Act Changing the Name of the Sebaste Central School in the Municipality of Sebaste, Province of Antique, to Juan O. Dela Cruz Memorial School
Section 1. The name of the Sebaste Central School in the Municipality of Sebaste, Province of Antique, is changed to Juan O. dela Cruz Memorial School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
